message: Hey! I'm good, thanks. How about you?
I'm doing pretty well, thanks. Did you see the new movie that just came out?
No, I haven't had a chance to yet. Is it any good?
Yeah, it's really good! I highly recommend it.
Cool, I'll have to check it out. Thanks for the recommendation!
No problem! Let me know what you think after you see it.
Will do. Hey, did you hear about the new restaurant that opened up downtown?
No, I haven't. What kind of food do they serve?
It's a Mexican restaurant. I heard the tacos are amazing!
